al/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網睇到好多人有不快經驗<br />\n我自己就家訪一次<br />\n接左貓貓之後再家訪一次之後就ok<br />\n而家貓貓都已經養左十年 so far都好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果怕麻煩或者唔鐘意俾太多個人資料人<br />\n我諗搵愛協果啲機構比較適合</blockquote><br />\n但見愛協個網都好似話要搵你屋企人又盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f2fbe949ccc13045fdc32e9790d29bd09445ca","tid":89230,"uid":7212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T01:16:13.000Z","msg":"我都想有正職後養貓，但好怕離別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif&h=4e2a94e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adabfb8f8819988f3fc1df3501f818c0527ca278","tid":89230,"uid":12765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想有正職後養貓，但好怕離別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif&h=4e2a94e2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都驚，會當左佢係屋企人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3270f04f0009ae512461c786aeed95ad8f9ee3","tid":89230,"uid":2839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想有正職後養貓，但好怕離別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://media.tumblr.com/tumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_mbad4pxtXF1qhp74a.gif&h=4e2a94e2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都驚，會當左佢係屋企人一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會傷心架, 預左架啦, 但我到時會再領養, 幫得一隻得一隻, 流浪貓好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9738d9581b260f8f43065bc5ad46e3de5c1588cf","tid":89230,"uid":2839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"我覺得, 最緊要佢在生時生活得開心. 生老病死冇得避既."}]}